{"tid":1617883,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【唔好忘記新屋嶺】急招前線做外媒訪問!!!","createTime":"2019-10-04T02:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T20:41:45.000Z","uid":259321,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3f4dc0e4824277cc20abf759bc8f61c6da9bce58","tid":1617883,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:34:07.000Z","msg":"10.1大單野<br />\n但新屋嶺被<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>輪姦</strong></span>被<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>虐待</strong></span><br />\n多宗<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>被浮屍被跳樓被吊頸</strong></span><br />\n慘烈情況絕對需要繼續跟進<br />\n我唔知新屋嶺慘案幾時先可以平反<br />\n小弟之前有幫手G20做文宣 (起我底睇返)<br />\n同外媒有過少量聯絡<br />\n宜家<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>法新社</strong></span>一位記者聯絡我<br />\n佢跟緊新屋嶺條線<br />\n想聯絡到前線做一個新屋嶺嘅訪問<br />\n急需要<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>***未入過***新屋嶺但有心理準備入嘅前線</strong></span>做呢個訪問!!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v5M4dh5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv5M4dh5.jpg&h=99a04638&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J6DVjX9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ6DVjX9.jpg&h=570f0f29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你係前線或者識人做前線<br />\n請加TG: <a href=\"https://t.me/sunukling\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsunukling&d=beIwg85N8Ddzcl6rIyS0GegAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=039d91f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sunukling</a><br />\n放心<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我唔會問你任何你嘅野</strong></span><br />\n只會講<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>關於個訪問</strong></span>同俾個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>記者嘅Contact</strong></span>你<br />\n請聯絡到之後叫佢證明自己係法新社記者嘅身份<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>請前線幫幫手跟進新屋嶺!!!</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d11bd1e216ef9dceb0184a80ff873fb8bd856f","tid":1617883,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:34:23.000Z","msg":"100"},{"pid":"f171aaf8d4bc4350237b28690dbafe97cd2b8398","tid":1617883,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:34:35.000Z","msg":"99"},{"pid":"aa39ff33c1cb90566dfafddd04fe64ac6a0f6f4d","tid":1617883,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:34:46.000Z","msg":"98"},{"pid":"5d2d05094f49c7e162e89c7b5b88430183010bc3","tid":1617883,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:35:45.000Z","msg":"97"},{"pid":"c69384515d351cffc0cd6c1f5bce04bb95e263cf","tid":1617883,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:35:55.000Z","msg":"96"},{"pid":"d841cf13a310bcca1f8750ad750451ef139a676c","tid":1617883,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:36:19.000Z","msg":"95"},{"pid":"8e5bcd0200ed8e8afc17f3c955dd690a1843f415","tid":1617883,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:37:20.000Z","msg":"94"},{"pid":"bdf9da8efa2d2fc4efb975e52f131ef7edca50db","tid":1617883,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:37:30.000Z","msg":"93"},{"pid":"25266046a46b9a7b22ed956d641164caf21b5d73","tid":1617883,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:38:04.000Z","msg":"92"},{"pid":"20a13328f975731b45a1cf661f4ee2ec0cbd4996","tid":1617883,"uid":67006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:38:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"819ca3e3716bd34e40788db26cb271ae2a582a50","tid":1617883,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:38:57.000Z","msg":"91"},{"pid":"d15847e34fb1